{"tid":1557492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：絕不認同外國議會干預香港內部事務","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T07:26:25.000Z","uid":147956,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62e9096bbb2fabfa1d9d7bb822d366934ea727ae","tid":1557492,"uid":147956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mN2vFvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmN2vFvU.jpg&h=caacd680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥指，對美國國會審議香港人權與民主法案感到深切遺憾，絕不認同外國議會干預香港內部事務。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，今次已非美國國會首次以審議香港人權與民主法案，介入特區事務，她認為特區事務應由特區政府處理，外國議會並非香港事務的持份者，以任何形式干預香港內部事務，都是極不恰當，她對此感到深切遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又希望，不會再有本地人士主動要求美國政府或國會，通過將會影響香港的人權與民主法案。"},{"pid":"189a8bd82350d922efbcf6491b7550f9e7cfe033","tid":1557492,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"起底---&gt;BLOCK--&gt;上一頁"},{"pid":"e636abf10f5e776ad5f3a8870dfd33e146b1e47d","tid":1557492,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"調番轉睇就知下一步應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美領 美領"},{"pid":"c2265622a25eaf4e4b99d8864bfc6d6b138704b6","tid":1557492,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"美國內政關你條八婆撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde8a45091efa00a310486d4afd2005edf42f557","tid":1557492,"uid":260668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"驚到腳軟了"},{"pid":"48c9a4c2353741bf342d32e21d52f6b6c526c8bf","tid":1557492,"uid":129531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"乜原來香港政府有權干預他國內政?<br />\n對他國事務說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04826a9eede1fce77c582c0f9cffbc88b4440455","tid":1557492,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"陳坤耀不斷提倡一個說法：把70年代財政司司長夏鼎基提倡的positive non-interventionism翻譯作「積極不干預」是大錯特錯。他指出：「港英年代的經濟哲學一向是最大的支持，最小的干預（maximum support，minimum intervention），即使是港英年代的財政司郭伯偉也不是提倡完全放任的政策。」但政府、傳媒、社會大眾翻譯為積極不干預，意思成為了「積極地」不干預，但這是翻譯的錯誤，應該是「積極性」的不干預，差之毫釐，謬以千里，一個錯誤，誤導政府官員及市民多年，實在令人咋舌，翻譯講求「信、達、雅」，重要性可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/%e9%99%b3%e5%9d%a4%e8%80%80%ef%bc%9a%e7%a9%8d%e6%a5%b5%e4%b8%8d%e5%b9%b2%e9%a0%90%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e8%a2%ab%e8%aa%a4%e8%a7%a3%e5%a4%9a%e5%b9%b4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%25e9%2599%25b3%25e5%259d%25a4%25e8%2580%2580%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%25a9%258d%25e6%25a5%25b5%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%25b9%25b2%25e9%25a0%2590%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25b9%25b4%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=d90bc7ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/%e9%99%b3%e5%9d%a4%e8%80%80%ef%bc%9a%e7%a9%8d%e6%a5%b5%e4%b8%8d%e5%b9%b2%e9%a0%90%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e8%a2%ab%e8%aa%a4%e8%a7%a3%e5%a4%9a%e5%b9%b4/</a><br />\n<br />\n有高度理由懷疑，港共中共因英文能力差，錯解左不干預政策，導致政策全球蹄笑皆非。"},{"pid":"116a4b4cd8cedd8feca5bb15f5c835fb8605c1a4","tid":1557492,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04826a9eede1fce77c582c0f9cffbc88b4440455","tid":1557492,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"陳坤耀不斷提倡一個說法：把70年代財政司司長夏鼎基提倡的positive non-interventionism翻譯作「積極不干預」是大錯特錯。他指出：「港英年代的經濟哲學一向是最大的支持，最小的干預（maximum support，minimum intervention），即使是港英年代的財政司郭伯偉也不是提倡完全放任的政策。」但政府、傳媒、社會大眾翻譯為積極不干預，意思成為了「積極地」不干預，但這是翻譯的錯誤，應該是「積極性」的不干預，差之毫釐，謬以千里，一個錯誤，誤導政府官員及市民多年，實在令人咋舌，翻譯講求「信、達、雅」，重要性可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/%e9%99%b3%e5%9d%a4%e8%80%80%ef%bc%9a%e7%a9%8d%e6%a5%b5%e4%b8%8d%e5%b9%b2%e9%a0%90%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e8%a2%ab%e8%aa%a4%e8%a7%a3%e5%a4%9a%e5%b9%b4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%25e9%2599%25b3%25e5%259d%25a4%25e8%2580%2580%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%25a9%258d%25e6%25a5%25b5%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%25b9%25b2%25e9%25a0%2590%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%25b9%25b4%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=d90bc7ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/%e9%99%b3%e5%9d%a4%e8%80%80%ef%bc%9a%e7%a9%8d%e6%a5%b5%e4%b8%8d%e5%b9%b2%e9%a0%90%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e8%a2%ab%e8%aa%a4%e8%a7%a3%e5%a4%9a%e5%b9%b4/</a><br />\n<br />\n有高度理由懷疑，港共中共因英文能力差，錯解左不干預政策，導致政策全球蹄笑皆非。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"外交部可能都係因為翻譯問題，以為不干預係世界共識外交政策，根本上理解錯不干預政策的意義"},{"pid":"7ed8cdef208d59f5e9ba04793e3e564d6052c22c","tid":1557492,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭憑咩野代表香港發言"},{"pid":"ecf122ed7813655398a4f83ae8e469beed3a99b0","tid":1557492,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:26:25.000Z","msg":"5日前既post你地班仆街推乜撚野<br />\n成班垃圾"}]}